{"id":612251,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/06/【网络民议】电影事业，可不能这么搞/","date":"2019-06-14T17:32:37Z","modified":"2019-06-15T11:46:59Z","title":"【网络民议】电影事业，可不能这么搞","content":"<p>编者按：原定6月15日晚在上海国际电影节作为开幕电影放映的《八佰》被取消，而其中网友推测是因为电影中有对抗日做出贡献的国民党和青天白日旗帜致敬的情节和镜头。为此，电影导演贾樟柯在微博发言说：电影事业，可不能这么搞。贾樟柯的发言得多许多网友的支持和感慨，有网友回复说：我们活在连屁都不敢放的体系里面。</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-612255\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/2-18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"281\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/2-18.jpg 1920w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/2-18-300x169.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/2-18-768x432.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/2-18-1024x576.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-612256\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/1-20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"889\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/1-20.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/1-20-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/1-20-768x1365.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/1-20-576x1024.jpg 576w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-612257\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/Capture1-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"638\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/Capture1-1.png 715w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/Capture1-1-235x300.png 235w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-612261\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/webwxgetmsgimg.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/webwxgetmsgimg.jpg 1440w, https: